	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身體好像在發燒，全身無力<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
早知道會這樣，<delay20 />
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就先買好<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />預備了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是有<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />的話，<delay8 />
