<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我就<delay8 />吃一點吧<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />這種東西，真是一點也不好吃啊。<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />感覺它開始發揮作用了咧。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦！？<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />體溫好像開始升高了！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好苦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
