<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />我覺得好像舒服點了。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說你<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
要是其實沒藥也無所謂啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你讓我抖得更厲害了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂喂喂<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />你沒有藥啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是無所謂啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但有點期望落空啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你給我<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />，我得送你謝禮。<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是<tag a="125" b="4" arg="0x0" />。<delay frames="40" />
不用客氣，儘管收下吧。</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">多虧有你，我得救啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對我來說，你可是恩人啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然算不上什麼謝禮，<delay20 />
但這個<tag a="125" b="4" arg="0x0" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就收下吧。</message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺身體越變越輕鬆了。<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />這種東西<delay8 />還真不得了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這<tag a="125" b="4" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
算是我的一點心意，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你能收下！</message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是我又生病，<delay20 />
到時候也要拜託你啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />俗話說得好，「遠親不如近鄰」。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，多謝你啊。<delay20 /></message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算是我，也承受不住這病痛。<10_4 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要<delay8 />多保重身體啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼～<delay8 />你真是幫了大忙<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，多謝啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我想好好答謝你，<delay20 />
但你的持有物品好像滿了所以拿不動。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚點我再寄去你家吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
